{"_path":"/councilor/service/s2062","_dir":"service","_draft":false,"_partial":false,"_locale":"","title":"質詢警察局有關地方議題","description":null,"image":"/images/service/s2062-1.png","sequence":2062,"category1":"A. 健全都市發展","category2":"A.1 加速宜居城市建設","link":"https://www.facebook.com/share/p/1ASdBRaM3f/","author":"李宗豪","head":{"meta":[{"name":"keywords","content":""},{"name":"robots","content":""},{"name":"author","content":"李宗豪"},{"name":"copyright","content":"© 2024 A7新林口-社區網站"},{"name":"og:title","content":"地方行政"}]},"publishedAt":"2025-05-06T00:00:00.000Z","toc":true,"body":{"type":"root","children":[{"type":"element","tag":"h2","props":{"id":"質詢警察局有關地方議題"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"質詢警察局有關地方議題"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"文青派出所加速建置"},{"type":"element","tag":"br","props":{},"children":[]},{"type":"text","value":"\n重劃區發展快速，至今仍沒有專責派出所，周邊派出所警力負擔沉重。我要求警察局加速規劃，強化巡邏與緊急應變能力。局長當場回應「會加速辦理」，我會持續緊盯進度。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"img","props":{"alt":"s2062-1.jpeg","src":"/images/service/s2062-1.jpeg"},"children":[]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"a","props":{"href":"https://tyenews.com/2025/05/843016/?fbclid=IwY2xjawKGpcBleHRuA2FlbQIxMABicmlkETFrajQ3dExGVnhOdzMyV09JAR6OfdKK9SAltPXm-QAje0wdIQ00qaRes-0zad8AIMSHYZewV42tZHZVH7khHA_aem_nWRk27xhlSrZVBwWdt4T9w"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"桃園電子報 2025/05/06"}]},{"type":"text","value":":\n"},{"type":"element","tag":"strong","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"龜山文青派出所預計明年發包 118 年完工啟用"}]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"李宗豪指出，龜山文青里、樂善里周邊，因居住人口快速攀升，已逐漸形成完整生活圈。然而，地方長期缺乏就近警力支援，緊急狀況處理及巡邏能量皆不足，已嚴重影響居民安全感。市府與警察局應盡速完成相關用地整備與規劃招標程序，讓派出所能早日動工啟用，強化當地治安。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"對此，吳坤旭回應，將會全力加速辦理文青派出所的設置事宜，目前正在規劃設計中，預計明(115)年發包施工，118 年完工啟用。"}]}],"toc":{"title":"","searchDepth":2,"depth":2,"links":[{"id":"質詢警察局有關地方議題","depth":2,"text":"質詢警察局有關地方議題"}]}},"_type":"markdown","_id":"content:councilor:service:s2062.md","_source":"content","_file":"councilor/service/s2062.md","_extension":"md"}